name: Vessels 190: Nibbler
description: Nibbler isn’t much of a kisser.  That is not armour in front of his jaw, that IS his jaw.  He got stomped on by a mech in a tournament fight and life has never been the same since.  He is very handy as a mechanic now though- his bite strength gives him almost an extra hand when he is at work. He also still loves to dance.
